OL,7,FLong-awaited laws banning the
OL,8,Fcreation of new leasehold properties
OL,9,Fis due to be introduced to Parliament
OL,10,Fon Monday.
OL,12,FThe Leasehold and Freehold Reform
OL,13,FBill will mark its first step on the
OL,14,Fpath to becoming legislation, hailed
OL,15,Fby Housing Secretary Michael Gove as
OL,16,Fa "landmark moment for millions."
OL,18,FOther than in exceptional
OL,19,Fcircumstances, new houses in England
OL,20,Fand Wales will be freehold from the
OL,21,Foutset, under the planned reforms.
